department: Chinese, South and Southeast Asian Art
description:
(Found in Collection, 7/24/95)
Necklace of dark brown wooden beads and four large evenly spaced green stone beads.  Two separate strands of green stones ending in purple and gold pendants hanging from right side.  Similar strand ending in green pendant hanging from left side.  A large green stone and blue band with a green pendant on the end hangs from bottom center of necklace.
title: Wood and Stone Beaded Necklace
